--Okarin... Oka--

6
00:00:19,250 --> 00:00:22,208
Where did Toranoana and Animate go?!

7
00:00:22,208 --> 00:00:24,125
Where's Mandarake and Gamers?!

8
00:00:24,125 --> 00:00:28,417
What are you talking about, Okarin?
You know there aren't any in Akiba.

9
00:00:28,417 --> 00:00:30,875
That's why Mayushii has
to go all the way to Nakano--

10
00:00:30,875 --> 00:00:34,958
Mayuri! You work
part-time at May Queen, right?!

11
00:00:34,958 --> 00:00:36,958
What's "May Queen"?

12
